results.name: Triangle T(g, h) = number of rotes of weight g and height h, both in gammas.
comment: T(g, h) = |{positive integers m : A062537(m) = g and A109301(m) = h}|.
Row sums = A061396. Column sums = A109300. See A111792 for details.
Main diagonal T(j, j) = 2^(j-1) for j > 0, T(0, 0) = 1.
